    "name": "怪物对决自走棋",
    "steam_appid": 3141720,
    "required_age": 0,
    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3141720/extras/9e91e997b0dfc813041631624ae6c41e.avif?t=1771657071\" width=600 height=128 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3141720/extras/805ad64b4e260d802e09faee2d555944.avif?t=1771657071\" width=616 height=65 /></span></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >每场战斗前排的怪兽会优先攻击和承受伤害，有些则优先攻击后排的怪兽。你将能够预测自己的攻击过程，让肉盾冲锋陷阵，还是让刺客秒杀后排，灵活派兵部将，探索更多玩法吧！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3141720/extras/323c4d7e82ea87a93e01e8b9937c4470.poster.avif?t=1771657071\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3141720/extras/323c4d7e82ea87a93e01e8b9937c4470.webm?t=1771657071\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3141720/extras/323c4d7e82ea87a93e01e8b9937c4470.mp4?t=1771657071\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3141720/extras/fe5655e88a1895c13f1bc84bb2bf54cc.avif?t=1771657071\" width=616 height=65 /></span></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >《怪物对决》的世界充满各种各样的神奇物种，不死族、野兽、亡灵、还有神秘的蛋...组合相同阵容的怪物，会发挥出更强的战力。不断探索、发掘出属于你的强力阵容！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3141720/extras/cf8c4dc6d1c4c4b788d8e958cec3feaf.poster.avif?t=1771657071\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3141720/extras/cf8c4dc6d1c4c4b788d8e958cec3feaf.webm?t=1771657071\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3141720/extras/cf8c4dc6d1c4c4b788d8e958cec3feaf.mp4?t=1771657071\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3141720/extras/9dedd011ab23cd0cbcd899e88bdab467.avif?t=1771657071\" width=616 height=65 /></span></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >不同的怪物之间会融合进化。将他们组合在一起，则会在下一回合进化成功，不断升级，成长为更强大的物种，进化成究极怪兽横扫战场吧！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3141720/extras/97697a2f998a442ea62e599667095442.poster.avif?t=1771657071\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3141720/extras/97697a2f998a442ea62e599667095442.webm?t=1771657071\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3141720/extras/97697a2f998a442ea62e599667095442.mp4?t=1771657071\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3141720/extras/66e82d4dd81b4c41ac7a51fa177aa170.avif?t=1771657071\" width=616 height=65 /></span></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >你将与其他玩家展开真实的对战，面对的是真实玩家的怪兽阵容。思考如何最大化利用现有的资源，不断优化阵容，直面愈来愈强的对手，拿下这一局！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3141720/extras/dcdd6e09f0376ff7656f8a25f43a814c.poster.avif?t=1771657071\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3141720/extras/dcdd6e09f0376ff7656f8a25f43a814c.webm?t=1771657071\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3141720/extras/dcdd6e09f0376ff7656f8a25f43a814c.mp4?t=1771657071\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
